  "factionId": "SM",
  "sourceId": "000000162",
  "legend": "With pinpoint accuracy, Gladiator Lancer crews use this battle tank’s laser destroyer to spear through the heaviest enemy armour and punch smouldering holes in the flesh ofxenos monstrosities. Such is the range of its heavy cannon that it can eliminate threats to the Black Templars before their battle-brothers encounter them, storming past their wrecks to seek the next affront to the Emperor.",
